ovde, kao sto cete cuti na Monmartru

3
00:00:20,070 --> 00:00:21,750
<i>cudna prica o...</i>

4
00:00:56,590 --> 00:01:00,910
<i>Prica pocinje u momentima 
izmedju noci i dana,</i>

5
00:01:01,270 --> 00:01:03,350
<i>u svitanje.</i>

6
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:06,190
<i>Montmartre je i raj...</i>

7
00:01:16,910 --> 00:01:18,670
<i>... i pakao.</i>

8
00:01:24,070 --> 00:01:26,030
<i>kao sto ce se pokazati.</i>

9
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:34,350
<i>Ljudi prolaze jedni pored drugih,
veciti stranci.</i>

10
00:01:34,430 --> 00:01:38,430
<i>Radni ljudi kao ova cistacica,
koja je jako stara,</i>

11
00:01:38,670 --> 00:01:41,470
<i>I besposlicari,
Kao ova mlada devojka,</i>

12
00:01:41,550 --> 00:01:44,350
<i>Koja je rano procvetala 
za svoje godine.</i>

13
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:04,390
<i>Ali hajdemo do Boba.
Bob Kockar.</i>

14
00:02:05,390 --> 00:02:08,190
<i>Mladoliki starac iz 
skorasnje proslosti....</i>

15
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,950
Ides u Carpeaux's?

16
00:03:13,070 --> 00:03:14,630
<i>Taxi, gospodine?</i>

17
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:17,110
<i>Izvinite, Mr. Bob,
Nisam vas prepoznao.</i>

18
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:23,270
Stvarno mutno lice.

19
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:16,670
<i>Da se provozamo na mojoj bicikli?</i>

20
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:00,830
<i>'jutro, Mr. Bob.</i>

21
00:05:15,470 --> 00:05:17,550
<i>Hvala, Mr. Bob.</i>

22
00:05:17,790 --> 00:05:19,790
<i>'noc, Pops.</i>

23
00:05:24,150 --> 00:05:26,110
- Kako si?
- Dobro.

24
00:05:26,550 --> 00:05:28,150
Ulazi.

25
00:05:29,350 --> 00:05:31,630
<i>Zdravo, gospodo.</i>

26
00:05:32,670 --> 00:05:34,670
Vi panduri nikada ne spavate.

27
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:36,710
Sta ako me vide sa tobom?

28
00:05:36,790 --> 00:05:38,470
- Kuda?
- Carpeaux's.

29
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:41,110
<i>- Na kockanje.
- Ne, samo da se pozdravim.</i>

30
00:05:41,990 --> 00:05:43,830
Vozi do Carpeaux's.

31
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:48,150
Ne ceo put.
Ne smes mi srusiti reputaciju.

32
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,630
<i>Evo nesto za citanje.</i>

33
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:19,110
Triling.

34
00:06:27,470 --> 00:06:28,790
Jedan cip.

35
00:06:32,030 --> 00:06:33,590
Odustejem.

36
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:38,190
Da li je ovo Bob, jedan od vasih dousnika?

37
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:41,910
<i>On? Ako te cuje da to kazes...
Ne, on je stari drugar.</i>

38
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:44,670
da li si cuo za slucaj trijumf?

39
00:06:44,710 --> 00:06:46,830
<i>Bilo je to pre tvog vremena.</i>

40
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:51,110
Jedne noci je Stick pucao na mene.
Bob mu je izbio pistolj.

41
00:06:51,190 --> 00:06:54,430
Zasto je to uradio?
Mozda zato sto sam bio nenaoruzan.

42
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:57,990
Ili da spasi Stick-a od dozivotne 
za ubistvo policajca.

43
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:00,270
Nikada nisam saznao razlog.

44
00:07:00,350 --> 00:07:02,550
Ali tog dana smo postali prijatelji.

45
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:06,950
- Nije li on smutljivac?
- Da, ali godine su ga opametile.

46
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:10,630
Nije li on opljackao Rimbaud Banku
Pre 20 godina?

47
00:07:10,910 --> 00:07:14,630
Jest'. Ali nije lezao za to.
To ga je umirilo.

48
00:07:29,910 --> 00:07:33,310
Odustani, Roger.
U igri sam.

49
00:07:33,430 --> 00:07:36,430
- Dakle vidim, Bob.
- Zasto me zoves Bob?

50
00:07:36,550 --> 00:07:38,670
Radis sve isto kao Bob.

51
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:41,390
Deca uvek nekog kopiraju.

52
00:07:42,150 --> 00:07:44,510
Pozuri, duso. Imas sastanak.

53
00:07:44,590 --> 00:07:46,390
- Sastanak?
- Pozuri!

54
00:07:47,430 --> 00:07:49,150
Vidimo se.

55
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,950
Uvek dzentlmen!

56
00:07:51,030 --> 00:07:53,310
Nikad posle zalaska.

57
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:03,350
Bacio si jos jedan svezanj.

58
00:08:03,470 --> 00:08:07,310
Zar nisi mogao da udjes posle onoga?

59
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:10,190
- Koliko?
- 200 dizem.

60
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:12,710
Treba mi pice.

61
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:15,070
Za mene ne. Prijavljujem se.
Pobedjen sam.

62
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,550
A pastis, Yvonne.

63
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,670
ON stoji u mestu.

64
00:08:25,030 --> 00:08:28,230
Mislim da blefira.
Pokazao sam svoja tri keca.

65
00:08:29,030 --> 00:08:31,430
Imao je ful.
- Sranje!

66
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:33,310
Mozes to ponoviti!

67
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:48,710
- Ne idem dalje?
- Treba da se vidim sa devojkom.

68
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:51,110
- Sa onom sto sam je upravo video?
- Ne, druga.

69
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:53,630
Preforsirao si.
Vazi, odlazi.

70
00:08:53,710 --> 00:08:55,430
Vidimo se veceras?

71
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:12,990
"Nemoj cistiti kucu danas.
Pusti me da spavam.

72
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:20,990
Stigao sam kasno sinoc."

73
00:11:00,990 --> 00:11:03,910
"da te nebi probudila, ostavi ves u kuhinji.

74
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:07,190
Imas svezu kafu na sporetu. Celeste."

75
00:11:13,030 --> 00:11:14,510
Marc.

76
00:11:16,710 --> 00:11:19,990
Moras mi pomoci.
Treba mi novac da odem iz grada.

77
00:11:20,470 --> 00:11:22,590
Pokusao sam te telefonirati.
- Udji.

78
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:29,150
Koliko?
- 100 clama.

79
00:11:29,230 --> 00:11:33,790
prebio sam Lydiu.
U bolnici je.

80
00:11:33,950 --> 00:11:37,110
Potkradala me je.
Vec sam joj dao fore.

81
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,470
- Gubi se!
- Sta?

82
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:44,390
Gubi se, cujes?

83
00:11:45,590 --> 00:11:47,230
Ali, Bob...

84
00:11:47,430 --> 00:11:50,870
Ja volim da pomognem ljudima u velikoj nevolji,
Ali takvima ko ti ne.

85
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:52,790
Sta je to sa tobom?

86
00:11:52,830 --> 00:11:54,790
ne volim makroe.

87
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:58,790
Mislio sam da si se opametio,
i da trgujes krpama.

88
00:11:59,430 --> 00:12:02,470
I imas petlje da mi se obratis?

89
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:05,710
Gubi se!

90
00:13:07,830 --> 00:13:09,190
Vec!

91
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:20,270
<i>Ne radi vam telefon, Gospodine.</i>

92
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:23,470
Moras se trgnuti.

93
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:26,670
Rekao sam ti,
obrisi usta maramicom.

94
00:13:26,750 --> 00:13:28,630
Sta ima?
- Nas randevu.

95
00:13:28,710 --> 00:13:30,910
Na putu sam!

96
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:32,790
Kasno je.

97
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:35,470
Vreme je da ides kuci Mama.

98
00:13:37,070 --> 00:13:40,710
Mr. Bob dolazi.
Samo o tome brines.

99
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:42,550
Vidimo se sutra?
- Zvacu te.

100
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:46,390
HEADS ORTAI LS BAR

101
00:13:56,110 --> 00:14:00,070
kako me sreca sluzi, 
cak bi i u decijoj igri izgubio.

102
00:14:09,430 --> 00:14:10,870
Izvin'te.

103
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:22,070
Trazis da zamenis Lydiu?

104
00:14:27,910 --> 00:14:31,230
- Ne treba mi cuvar.
- Ne, samo dobar udarac.

105
00:14:32,190 --> 00:14:35,310
Zar ne znas da su sporedne
ulice u Rimu opasne?

106
00:14:35,390 --> 00:14:37,230
Ti stitis udovice i sirocad?

107
00:14:37,310 --> 00:14:39,830
Reci jos nesto tako i udaricu te.

108
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:41,350
Usudi se!

109
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:44,950
Kasno si nocu za svoje godine.

110
00:14:45,030 --> 00:14:46,630
Nocna skola.

111
00:14:49,430 --> 00:14:50,870
Ostavi to.

112
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:53,710
Smesti je za nas sto.

113
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:55,230
Hajde, dete.

114
00:15:00,350 --> 00:15:02,790
- Kako se zoves?
- Anne.

115
00:15:02,870 --> 00:15:04,870
Paulo... Anne.

116
00:15:04,950 --> 00:15:08,470
Moja devojka iz snova! Ako samo kaze da,
Sreca ce joj se okrenuti.

117
00:15:08,550 --> 00:15:10,470
Ne pocinji! Dete je gladno.

118
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:14,150
Yvonne, Cujes ovo? Dete je gladno.

119
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:20,550
Ja sam zgodan, zar ne?

120
00:15:20,630 --> 00:15:21,990
Zavrsio si?

121
00:15:22,070 --> 00:15:24,430
kako mozes gladovati uz takve oci?

122
00:15:24,470 --> 00:15:28,470
Mislio sam da lutke poput tebe, 
sve imaju divne dadilje.

123
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:30,830
Upravo sam nasao jednu.

124
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:33,990
Zasto se muvas oko
Montmartrea?

125
00:15:34,070 --> 00:15:36,070
Zar nemas posao?

126
00:15:36,150 --> 00:15:38,110
Imala sam.

127
00:15:38,190 --> 00:15:41,510
- i?
- Sef nije bio idealan muskarac.

128
00:15:41,590 --> 00:15:44,190
Cujem idealan!

129
00:15:44,270 --> 00:15:45,830
Sta si ostavila?

130
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:48,230
Uvek spavas sama?

131
00:15:48,310 --> 00:15:50,470
Skoro uvek.

132
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:53,270
Ne muvaj se po Montmartreu, dete.

133
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:56,070
Zavrsit ces kao ulicna princeza.

134
00:15:56,150 --> 00:15:58,790
Da li devojka kao ti treba 
da ostaje ovako kasno?

135
00:15:58,830 --> 00:15:59,790
Sta?

136
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:02,870
Video sam te u nekom smecu, jedes pomfrit.

137
00:16:02,950 --> 00:16:05,150
Volim pomfrit.

138
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:09,550
Sta te to privlaci u ovom kraju?

139
00:16:09,630 --> 00:16:12,030
Lako je.
Svetla. Velika kola.

140
00:16:12,110 --> 00:16:14,270
Muzika u nocnim klubovima.

141
00:16:24,990 --> 00:16:27,510
10:00 sati! Imam sastanak.

142
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:30,190
Videcemo se opet?
- Zasto da ne?

143
00:16:30,270 --> 00:16:31,910
Vidimo se kasnije.

144
00:16:33,470 --> 00:16:36,470
- Tvoj prijatelj je fin.
- Fin mali covek.

145
00:16:37,430 --> 00:16:38,870
Racun!

146
00:16:43,670 --> 00:16:46,990
Koliko?
- 80.

147
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:52,270
Sta cemo sad?

148
00:16:52,350 --> 00:16:54,190
Mi?

149
00:16:54,270 --> 00:16:55,550
Vrema je za krevet.

150
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:57,990
kod tebe?

151
00:17:00,990 --> 00:17:04,030
- Imas li novca?
- Dosta. 300 franaka.

152
00:17:07,310 --> 00:17:10,030
Uzmi sobu u hotelu. 'Noc, mala.

153
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:14,150
<i>- Laku noc, Bob.
- 'Noc, Yvonne.</i>

154
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:22,390
Ajde.

155
00:17:22,430 --> 00:17:24,350
Ti cekaj ispred!

156
00:17:32,230 --> 00:17:33,710
Tu si dakle!

157
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:37,550
Sedi.

158
00:17:39,870 --> 00:17:41,950
  Sad pricaj.
- Nemam sta reci.

159
00:17:42,030 --> 00:17:43,270
Stvarno?

160
00:17:43,350 --> 00:17:46,150
Onda cu te uhapsiti za podvodjenje.

161
00:17:46,230 --> 00:17:50,110
Znas li kako prolaze povratnici?
Ti si mrtvo meso.

162
00:17:50,150 --> 00:17:52,430
Ali ja radim. Prodajem kanape.

163
00:17:52,470 --> 00:17:55,510
- Izvesnoj Lydi?
- Ona mi je devojka, Lieutenant!

164
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:58,590
Cudan si sa zenskama.

165
00:17:58,670 --> 00:18:00,510
Bio sam u bedaku.

166
00:18:00,590 --> 00:18:02,910
Dobro, ali to je gotovo.

167
00:18:02,990 --> 00:18:05,750
Vidis da placam porez.

168
00:18:05,830 --> 00:18:07,670
Ja sam radan covek.

169
00:18:07,710 --> 00:18:09,870
Ne mozes me optuziti za podvodjenje.

170
00:18:09,950 --> 00:18:14,150
"Ko prizna da zivi sa prostitutkom
ne moze poreci da nije podvodac."

171
00:18:15,030 --> 00:18:16,390
To je novi zakon!

172
00:18:17,550 --> 00:18:18,950
Sem ako...

173
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:21,390
- ako...?
- ne sredim stvari.

174
00:18:21,430 --> 00:18:23,550
- Molim te, Lieutenant!
- Ne tako brzo!

175
00:18:23,630 --> 00:18:27,150
Srecnice.
Lydia nece da se zali.

176
00:18:27,230 --> 00:18:29,670
Izlazi sutra iz bolnice.

177
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:32,390
Pusicu te pod jednim uslovom.

178
00:18:32,430 --> 00:18:34,390
Bilo sta, Lieutenant!

179
00:18:34,470 --> 00:18:36,630
Daj mi trag. Dobar!

180
00:18:36,670 --> 00:18:38,750
Ali ja nista ne znam.
Kunem se.

181
00:18:39,670 --> 00:18:42,430
Sem dvojce, trojce makroa.

182
00:18:42,470 --> 00:18:47,030
Ja nisam na tom odeljenju.
Hocu nesto veliko.

183
00:18:47,070 --> 00:18:48,550
Nista onda.

184
00:18:48,630 --> 00:18:50,510
Ne radi to!

185
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:54,990
Sad nemam nista,
ali cu naci nesto. Kunem se.

186
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:58,750
- Obecavas?
- Kunem se, Lieutenant!

187
00:18:58,830 --> 00:19:00,350
Mozes da ides.

188
00:19:04,350 --> 00:19:05,950
Ne zaboravi me.

189
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:08,390
Ili ...

190
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:19,030
- Dakle?
- Priznali su da su pogresili.

191
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:21,230
Odlicno. Sad necu morati da ti saljem paket.

192
00:19:24,350 --> 00:19:27,030
Crvena vina.
Ja cu se sakriti, ti trazi.

193
00:19:33,670 --> 00:19:36,230
Ovo.

194
00:19:36,310 --> 00:19:38,190
Po prvi put, mogao sam pobediti.

195
00:19:38,270 --> 00:19:40,510
Uradio sam ovo pre tebe.

196
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:43,390
Pogledaj ovo mesto!

197
00:19:43,430 --> 00:19:45,390
Kakva rupa!

198
00:19:45,470 --> 00:19:47,870
Dovoljno da osetis setno.
Da se razdvojimo!

199
00:19:47,950 --> 00:19:50,990
Ne mozemo svi imati duplex.
Ja nisam umetnik.

200
00:19:51,070 --> 00:19:52,750
A sad!

201
00:19:52,830 --> 00:19:54,190
Nisi klasa?

202
00:19:54,230 --> 00:19:57,110
Ja? Da li si zavrsio sa smejanjem?

203
00:19:57,150 --> 00:19:59,630
Nisam nista rekao! ludace?

204
00:19:59,710 --> 00:20:01,270
Ne jos, Ali ako ovako nastavi...

205
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:04,710
Shvatam, mala je u pitanju.
Ostavila te?

206
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:07,030
Ona bi ostavila svakog?

207
00:20:07,110 --> 00:20:09,350
hajdemo! Uzecu nam flasu.

208
00:20:09,430 --> 00:20:11,950
- ja placam sledecu!
- Obojcu cu vas sludeti.

209
00:20:11,990 --> 00:20:13,710
Ruke!

210
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:16,110
Reci, srca mi se vraca!

211
00:20:21,190 --> 00:20:23,230
- Da li su kola spremna?
- Tamo, Mr. Bob.

212
00:20:23,310 --> 00:20:26,070
- Benzin, ulje?
- Sve je spremno, Mr. Bob.

213
00:21:04,870 --> 00:21:06,310
Pigalle, molim te?

214
00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:10,910
Ti!

215
00:21:11,950 --> 00:21:13,390
Ulazi.

216
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:21,950
Sta ce ti kofer?
Prodajes pertle?

217
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:23,470
Ne. Selim se.

218
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:27,390
Vlasnik hotela ima glupa pravila:
Hoce pare u napred.

219
00:21:27,430 --> 00:21:31,470
Ljudi kojima dugujes novac uvek 
imaju glupa pravila.

220
00:21:32,070 --> 00:21:33,470
A 100 sam ti dao?

221
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:37,550
Platicu racun da bih uzeo svoje stvari.

222
00:21:37,630 --> 00:21:39,310
Sve su ti stvari tamo?

223
00:21:40,990 --> 00:21:42,390
Gde ces veceras?

224
00:21:42,470 --> 00:21:44,790
Ne znam ni sam.

225
00:21:44,830 --> 00:21:47,230
- Hoces kod mene?
- Vazi.

226
00:21:47,910 --> 00:21:50,950
Onda se odmori.
Imas dom.

227
00:22:19,670 --> 00:22:22,350
<i>LAk je broj:
36, kao kej.</i>

228
00:22:22,430 --> 00:22:24,950
<i>-Kej?
- ... des Orfèvres. Police HQ</i>

229
00:22:31,030 --> 00:22:32,310
Osecaj se kao kod kuce.

230
00:22:33,390 --> 00:22:36,110
- Tvoja porodica je sigurno bogata.
- Nije da nije.

231
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:40,750
- Cime se bavite?
- Ministarstvo poljoprivrede.

232
